# Get from your AnuraGate dashboard → Settings → API Keys
GATE_KEY=gk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Optional
# Model — any model on your AnuraGate key (e.g. gpt-4o, gemini-2.0-flash)
MODEL=
SYSTEM_PROMPT=You are a helpful travel and shopping assistant. Help the user find and book flights, hotels, and make purchases. When you identify something specific to purchase, describe the item, merchant, and price clearly before proceeding.

# One-time dashboard setup required before running this example:
#   1. Pro or higher plan
#   2. Dashboard → Finance → Wallets → create a wallet with a spend limit
#   3. Dashboard → Finance → Approver → set your approver (WhatsApp, Slack, or Telegram)
#   4. Have that platform's watcher running (see whatsapp/, slack/, or telegram/)
